com.vmware.nsx.fabric

Class FabricFactory

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.vmware.nsx.fabric.FabricFactory

  • public class FabricFactory
extends Object
    FabricFactory is responsible for creating instances of services contained inside the com.vmware.nsx.fabric package and also has the subpackages reference to access respective subpackage services.
